*** REQUIREMENT"

Education:
B.S. in Engineering or above.

Technical Profile:
• >5 years of proven design supplier quality engineering experience;
• Knowledge of ISO9001/14001;
• Experience in support global projects;
• Experience with quality tools( SPC,MSA, acceptance sampling, FMEA,PPAP etc.)
• Demonstrated strong analytical and problem solving skills;
• Knowledge of manufacturing quality system and working in regulated industry ;
• Experience on supplier quality management measurement practice;
• Experience on surface treatment process is preferred;
• Experience with geometric dimensioning and tolerance ;
• Working knowledge of Microsoft software.

Critical Competences:
Strong communication and leadership skill, able to communicate issues between internal organizations and external , able to consolidate the FACTS and lead on problem solving practice.

